00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Users can edit their own
posts at any time.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.500 line:80% position:20% align:start
By clicking "Edit", the text becomes
editable within the post card.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:13.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
The content is corrected and "Save"
is pressed to apply the changes.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:17.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
The post is immediately updated
with the new text.